{"tid":940640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人講一個風氣好差既台","createTime":"2018-12-14T05:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T08:31:18.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf02c5334c114a751e557588798371e21694e36","tid":940640,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"我拋磚先 講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入面有好多小圈子 你只要得罪過佢地<br />\n就以後唔駛再喺裏面立足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你走去寫故？佢地會出盡力唱衰你，例如狂比負評，等其他巴打都覺得你個故係好差，然後順勢都負評埋一份，你出聲問點解佢地盡量都唔會講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等你寫寫下無人睇而覺得心灰，久而久之自動收皮，唔好阻住佢地搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢地搞咁多野為乜呀，依家兩登寫故寫到出書嗰支歌仔已經無得唱咁濟，你地搞死其他新起步巴打，都唔會幫到自己出書，算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6671e52120abaedc91bbb3f46d4cb64ebc31994f","tid":940640,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"成人台"},{"pid":"07b156504611ff020f2c1ef6da362e615838d72c","tid":940640,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"體育台=波台"},{"pid":"bea7dabe1253146a8277440471963e2506554b1d","tid":940640,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b0958cca3a3cdf5d2a6baeaa651c6c8561d4c7d","tid":940640,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:31:18.000Z","msg":"樂士佛臺"}]}